<p class="text">
	The system is a web service, but we decided to write standalone client to make work
	with it more easier. We used Mozilla XUL Runner with my redesigned interface.
	So we threw away out all unnecessary things in browser and added a lot of cool features.
</p>

<p class="text">
	In addition, we developed a lot of other useful stuff: notifications, event logs,
	calendar, search, history, file versions and etc.
</p>

<p class="text">
	During this process of system developing I was responsible for user interface design
	and user experience. In total I designed and prototyped each of page for each department
	with own fields and actions and with dozens of unique working processes.
</p>
